data.description: Tehachapi City Charmer!!  This beautiful home has so much to offer!  Split-wing floor plan with multiple living spaces make it perfect whether you're up-sizing, down-sizing or buying your first home.  Built in 2007, it has 3 BD / 2 BA with 1,950 SF.  Living room with high ceilings and corner rock fireplace, separate office area, family room with slider to the back yard, breakfast nook and kitchen with an abundance of cabinets, custom tile countertops, breakfast bar, stainless-steel appliances and an adjacent laundry room with pantry and additional storage.  Spacious primary suite with walk-in closet, dual vanities, separate tub and shower, and a slider to the back yard.  Two guest bedrooms and main bath on a separate wing.  Natural gas, sewer and extremely affordable Tesla solar lease at roughly $80/month currently.  Come check out this great property and see why it's not just a house, it's your home!
